### Test get messages - CLIENT user (userId 1)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/chat/rooms/1/messages?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CLIENT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test get messages - ADMIN user
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/chat/rooms/1/messages?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get user info to verify userId
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
